g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: _ora-two-get-state (Target:class object ,OMO:class ora-two-manager-object) = (symbol) node-State:symbol = the symbol _an-ora-two-in-transition-object-of; begin if Target is _an-ora-two-poll-fail-object-of OMO then node-State = the symbol _an-ora-two-POLL-FAIL-OBJECT-OF else if Target is _an-ora-two-predicted-fail-object-of OMO then node-State = the symbol _an-ora-two-PREDICTED-FAIL-OBJECT-OF else if Target is _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of OMO then node-State = the symbol _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of; return node-State; end

c.PROTOOLS-DOCUMENTATION-DETAILS.ua.PROTOOLS-DESCRIPTION:
This repersents the relationship between an ORA Two manager object and an object in the domain that is considered to be a root cause failure,
'An object may be _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object, More than one object may be _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of an ora-two-manager-object

g2:Structure.g2:sa.DESCRIPTION: An object that root cause from the viewpoint of an ORA Two manager
An ORA Two manager that has objects that are root causes
An object may be _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object
More than one object may be _an-ora-two-root-cause-object-of an ora-two-manager-object

c.PROTOOLS-DOCUMENTATION-DETAILS.ua.PROTOOLS-DESCRIPTION:
This repersents the relationship between an ORA Two manager object and an object in the domain that failed a poll,
'An object may be _an-ora-two-poll-fail-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object, More than one object may be _an-ora-two-poll-fail-object-of an ora-two-manager-object'

g2:Structure.g2:sa.DESCRIPTION: An object that has a poll fail from the viewpoint of an ORA Two manager
An ORA Two manager that has objects that failed to poll
An object may be _an-ora-two-poll-fail-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object
More than one object may be _an-ora-two-poll-fail-object-of an ora-two-manager-object

c.PROTOOLS-DOCUMENTATION-DETAILS.ua.PROTOOLS-DESCRIPTION:
This repersents the relationship between an ORA Two manager object and an object in the domain that is predicted to fail a poll,
'An object may be _an-ora-two-predicted-fail-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object, More than one object may be _an-ora-two-predicted-fail-object-of an ora-two-manager-object'

g2:Structure.g2:sa.DESCRIPTION: An object that is predicted to fail from the viewpoint of an ORA Two manager
An ORA Two manager that has objects that are predicted to fail
An object may be _an-ora-two-predicted-fail-object-of more than one ora-two-manager-object
More than one object may be _an-ora-two-predicted-fail-object-of an ora-two-manager-object
Delay between checks to determine if poll is complete, i.e. 'Wait for poll to complete checking every ora-two-poll-complete-test-interval.'
Flag to indicate if predicted to fail objects will be polled to determine health when the root cause of the predicted fail is recovered.
